author: dims
msg: initial checkin for a skeleton jaxb schema generator. the idea is to collect the list of all the classes corresponding to the parameters and return types etc for all the methods, generate their schema using jaxbri schemagen and then call DefaultSchemaGenerator's generateSchemas to add whatever else is needed for the element wrappers for each method etc.
